target: TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_SEQ_00<tab>シルフの仮宿のトナクシアは、困っていることがあるようだ。

source: TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_SEQ_01<tab>Tonaxia has entrusted you with recovering several sacks of devil gourds─an invaluable source of dye for the sylphs' weaving─that she dropped when spooked by a pack of touched sylphs. Travel to Larkscall and search for the missing goods before the touched ones carry them away.
target: TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_SEQ_01<tab>トナクシアの依頼を受けた。ラークスコールにある、5つの「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E890B01 /var>」を入手しよう。

source: TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_SEQ_02<tab>You have successfully recovered the missing gourds. Deliver them to Tonaxia, who is sure to be pleased at this development.
target: TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_SEQ_02<tab><var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E890B01 /var>を入手した。シルフの仮宿の「トナクシア」に、「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E890B01 /var>」を渡そう。

source: TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_SEQ_03<tab>Tonaxia is overjoyed at the return of her gourds, and promises to return the favor at some unspecified time in the future. Temper your expectations, and continue to go about your business.
target: TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_SEQ_03<tab>トナクシアに<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E890B01 /var>を渡した。トナクシアは、大切なカボチャが戻ってきたことを大いに喜んでいるようだ。またの機会に協力しよう。

source: TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TODO_00<tab>Retrieve sacks of devil gourds from Larkscall.
target: TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TODO_00<tab>ラークスコールの<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E890B01 /var>を入手

source: TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TODO_01<tab>Deliver sacks of devil gourds to Tonaxia.

TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TONAXIA_000_000<tab>Woe, woe is this one! The peck of pumpkins that this one picked was purloined by a pack of pernicious ones! Or rather, this one dropped the sacks when startled by those ones.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TONAXIA_000_000<tab>うう……悔しいでふっち。
悪い子シルフたちに、カボチャを盗られたでふっち……。

source: TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TONAXIA_000_001<tab>The flesh of ripened devil gourds produces a most striking yellow dye for weaving. Without it, these ones' cloth will be reduced to dreary rags!
target:
TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TONAXIA_000_001<tab>熟した「オニカボチャ」は、とってもきれいなので、
糸を黄色に染めるときの必需品なのでふっち。
……それをあいつら、ひどい嫌がらせなのでふっち！

source: TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TONAXIA_000_002<tab>This one dropped gourds in Larkscall, near touched ones' home.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TONAXIA_000_002<tab>やつらは、カボチャを「ラークスコール」のどこかに隠して、
仲間を集めて持ち帰るつもりでふっち。
でも、今ならまだ間に合うでふっち！

source: TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TONAXIA_000_003<tab>Walking one must hurry and collect the gourds before touched ones carry them all away!
target:
TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TONAXIA_000_003<tab>悪い子シルフがシルフ領に持ち帰る前に、
「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E890B01 /var>」を、
取り返してきてほしいでふっち！

source: TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TONAXIA_000_010<tab>Walking one must hurry to Larkscall and retrieve this one's gourds before touched ones carry them all away!
target:
TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TONAXIA_000_010<tab>「ラークスコール」のどこかに隠されてる、
「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E890B01 /var>」を、
取り返してきてほしいでふっち！

source: TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TONAXIA_000_020<tab>There were five sacks of gourds, yes? Please tell this one you found them all!
target:
TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TONAXIA_000_020<tab>「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E890B01 /var>」はあったでふっち？
わたぴの覚えてるかぎり、5袋あるはずなのでふっち。

source: TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TONAXIA_000_030<tab>This one's gourds! Walking one is such strong and helpful one─nothing like another walking one this one knows. This one cannot believe these two are both walking ones.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TONAXIA_000_030<tab>ふっちっち！　ありがとでふっち～！
大事な大事なカボチャ、戻ってきたでふっち！

source: TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TONAXIA_000_031<tab>This one will weave beautiful dress for helpful one someday. But today, this one is busy one!
target:
TEXT_BANSYL103_01259_TONAXIA_000_031<tab>本当に助かったでふっち。
さすがは冒険者でふっち！
……同じヒトでも誰かさんとは大違いでふっち。
